Package: RforMath1110
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Tutorials for a First Course in Applied Statistics
Version: 0.1.2
Author: Adam Gilbert and A. Mia Heissan
Maintainer: The package maintainer: <a.heissan@mville.edu>
Description: This package deploys interactive tutorials for a first course in applied statistics. It follows the OpenIntro Statistics textbook and includes several resources adapted from that project.
